{"tid":1831594,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★穆迪降滙豐及恒生存款評級展望至負面","createTime":"2020-01-20T13:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T03:36:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4dc4806668ccc2a1ea99347e455b68fc400ad1ca","tid":1831594,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T13:23:40.000Z","msg":"投資評級公司穆迪發表報告，確定滙豐銀行及恒生銀行（0011）「Aa2」存款評級，短期評級為「P-1」。穆迪指出，受經濟放緩，在<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港及其他地區經營環境更困難，同時將兩行評級展望，由「穩定」降至「負面」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n穆迪指出香港示威活動正破壞消費及旅遊業，加上中美之間貿易緊張局勢，增加區內經濟前景不確定性，對滙豐及恒生資產質量及盈利能力帶來壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/411249/%E7%A9%86%E8%BF%AA%E9%99%8D%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E5%8F%8A%E6%81%92%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%98%E6%AC%BE%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A%E5%B1%95%E6%9C%9B%E8%87%B3%E8%B2%A0%E9%9D%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F411249%2F%25E7%25A9%2586%25E8%25BF%25AA%25E9%2599%258D%25E6%25BB%2599%25E8%25B1%2590%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%2581%2592%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25AD%2598%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E8%25A9%2595%25E7%25B4%259A%25E5%25B1%2595%25E6%259C%259B%25E8%2587%25B3%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E9%259D%25A2&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV95NY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=b1a0db3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/411249/%E7%A9%86%E8%BF%AA%E9%99%8D%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E5%8F%8A%E6%81%92%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%98%E6%AC%BE%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A%E5%B1%95%E6%9C%9B%E8%87%B3%E8%B2%A0%E9%9D%A2</a>"},{"pid":"10b1b8fb248e2cea7d345c78a9f6b5079e95e36d","tid":1831594,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T13:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f